'''''Gauche caviar''''' is a [[French language|French]] term to describe someone who claims to be a [[socialist]] without feeling the need to espouse an appropriate lifestyle. It implies that the person is less than sincere in their beliefs.

Similar terms in other countries include [[limousine liberal]], [[chardonnay socialist]], [[champagne socialist]]. Hypocrisy is implied.

